snippet.title: The Patchmaker's Workshop - F3 Trailer
snippet.description:
The Patchmaker's Workshop is a SM64 ROM Hack focused around abilities that Mario obtains in brand-new levels. Explore a forgotten story about life and creation when the hack releases in January 2025

Discord: https://discord.gg/4SZPveH
